Package io.curiositycore.thecuriositycore.commands.executables

Class CommandExecutable

java.lang.Object
io.curiositycore.thecuriositycore.commands.executables.CommandExecutable
public abstract class CommandExecutable extends Object
Abstract to define the generalisation of any executable within a command within a Curiosity Core Plugin. This generalisation applies to any type of command executable (including sub-executables).
(Supplementary interfaces can be utilised to add additional functionality to these executables)

    • determineTabCompletes

      protected abstract List<String> determineTabCompletes(String[] trueCommandArgs)
      Abstract method to define the generalisation of determining the tab completes for the executable if there are no other sub-executables to choose from a layer down from this executable.
      Parameters:
      trueCommandArgs - The true arguments for this specific executable.
      Returns:
      The tab completes to be sent to the Player.
